@QuizAPI_HostAddress = https://localhost:5001
@AdminToken = REPLACE_WITH_JWT

### Login
POST {{QuizAPI_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "Email": "admin@example.com",
  "Password": "REPLACE_WITH_PASSWORD"
}

### Upload Sample Package
POST {{QuizAPI_HostAddress}}/api/import/upload-package
Authorization: Bearer {{AdminToken}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----CodexBoundary

------CodexBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="File"; filename="sample-import-package.zip"
Content-Type: application/zip

< D:\Quiz_Application\QuizAPI\Samples\ImportPackage\sample-import-package.zip
------CodexBoundary--

### Process Returned CSV File
POST {{QuizAPI_HostAddress}}/api/import/process/REPLACE_WITH_UPLOADED_CSV_FILENAME
Authorization: Bearer {{AdminToken}}

### List Imported Quiz
GET {{QuizAPI_HostAddress}}/api/quiz?category=Safety
Accept: application/json

### Fetch Randomized Imported Quiz
GET {{QuizAPI_HostAddress}}/api/quiz/REPLACE_WITH_IMPORTED_QUIZ_ID/random
Accept: application/json
